## Common Template IDs Reference

| Template Name    | Template ID                            | Purpose                        |
|------------------|----------------------------------------|--------------------------------|
| Template         | `ab86861a-6030-46c5-b394-e8f99e8b87db` | Base for custom templates      |
| Template Section | `e269fbb5-3750-427a-9149-7aa950b49301` | Groups fields within template  |
| Template Field   | `455a3e98-a627-4b40-8035-e683a0331ac7` | Individual field definition    |
| JSON Rendering   | `04646a89-996f-4ee7-878a-ffdbf1f0ef0d` | Headless component rendering   |
| Folder           | `a87a00b1-e6db-45ab-8b54-636fec3b5523` | Organizing items               |
| JSS Data         | `a29d272e-9d48-453c-9e9d-b47585fa7f20` | Data folder for SXA sites      |
| _HorizonDatasourceGrouping | `D0F6BE14-2A2D-4C56-ACB5-80CAA573B8E2` | Enables child management in Pages Content tab (SXA) |

